#

Italian Pork Saltimbocca

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Pork

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

ItalianQuick MealPorkSavory

Description

Tender pork cutlets wrapped in prosciutto, sautéed, and finished with a white wine sauce for a flavorful Italian classic.

Ingredients

  • pork cutlets: 4 pieces
  • prosciutto: 4 slices
  • fresh sage leaves: 8 leaves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • white wine: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
